Maintainer: Stephen Early <steve@assorted.org.uk>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 11.0.0), debhelper-compat (= 11)
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Homepage: https://github.com/sde1000/quicktill-nfc-bridge

Package: quicktill-nfc-bridge
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3-pyscard (>= 1.9), pcscd (>= 1.8),
  python3-sdnotify, python3-libevdev
Description: Convert NFC card taps to quicktill user tokens
 quicktill-nfc-bridge converts NFC card taps on CCID-compatible NFC
 card readers into quicktill user tokens delivered as UDP packets to
 localhost:8455.
